text.tspan: Oh boy, now THIS thing is somebody who deserves to
stay in that cage of theirs for the rest of time. The
wizard who trapped Trouble dropped them off at this
mansion about seven years ago with a note with only
three words: "NEVER OPEN IT." I, uh, I got curious,
& brought hell upon the mansion as a result. They set,
like, eight different fires inside the mansion the span of
five minutes, and almost caused the mansion to just go
and collapse. Anyway, Anastasia re-trapped them and
that was that. No clue what we would do without her.
I learned my lesson that day, though.
